snippet.title: Amber Heard RUINS her Case AGAINST DEPP, LOSING in the DETAILS!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard RUINS her Case AGAINST DEPP, LOSING in the DETAILS! 

Heard's ENTIRE case rests on one idea: "The MONSTER." If "The Monster" doesn't exist, then the case with her or the Sun doesn't exist. THIS deposition, in my opinion, is one of the MOST IMPORTANT because it hits that, and THE MOST IGNORED because people miss its impact.
